data.description: This exceptional home, nestled in the sought-after Eaglebrooke Country Club Community, is a must-see. Gated community with 24 hour manned security situated on a quiet cul-de-sac, this home offers several updates that make it stand out from the rest. Enjoy the evenings soaking in the sounds of nature on your screened lanai. Expansive backyard with fully enclosed privacy fencing with beautiful oak tree on side yard creating a park like feel. Plenty of room for a pool & outdoor kitchen! Top of the line luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the home adds to its charm, and is super easy to maintain. Elegant crown molding in the entertaining spaces, recessed lighting, and beautiful arched windows that pour natural light into the formal living and dining room area. Fresh interior paint throughout and epoxy garage floors in the spacious 2 car garage. The floor plan is versatile and includes a formal living and dining room and 12x12 study/office suite. The primary suite is your private oasis, offering three large windows that let in plenty of natural light, spacious walk-in closets, and an en-suite bathroom with two separate vanities, exuding luxury. The property also includes a remodeled kitchen 2019 that boasts newer stainless steel appliances, a double oven, and granite countertops. New windows installed in 2021. All bathrooms were remodeled in 2019, new A/C 2019, and the roof replaced in 2017. Additionally, this home is equipped with a central vac system for your convenience! Built solid originally with upgrades for peace of mind. Plenty of parking on the street for your guests! Take a quick ride over to the clubhouse just down the street and part take in golf on one of Lakelands best golf courses or tennis, swimming and many other social activities as well as excellent Dining right in your own neighborhood. Easy access to shopping, restaurants & entertainment. Sellers are relocating, this is not a flip house. **Buyers to verify all room sizes**
